These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
House: cottage, craftsman, gothic-revival, art-deco
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the art-deco house##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching satire movies and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| House         | art-deco      | cottage | craftsman | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, march, june
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the mexican##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Birthday     | june        | march  | may    | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, lemon, tomato
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, coffee, almond-milk
1. the german is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating tomato##2
2. the argentine is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person eating kiwi and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi   | tomato     | lemon     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Beverage     | almond-milk      | sprite | coffee | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, april, june
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Birthday   | april  | june      | march        | may     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

