.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
House: futuristic, palace, ranch-style, colonial
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the futuristic house##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the colonial house and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the colonial house is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the palace house is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the colonial house is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the futuristic house is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| House   | ranch-style     | palace | colonial   | futuristic     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goat         | horse         | guinea-pig |

