3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to miami is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
